text:
Hehe...! It was just so cute...! I couldn't resist...!
I bought it with the intention of sharing it with everyone.

Since Luca-chan is coming today... let's divide it into four
portions...! Oh, can I take a picture before cutting it?

Yes...!
Who wants a piece of Hinamatsuri cake~

Since Haruki-chan bought it,
it's okay if Haruki-chan takes it all, right?

Thanks~. But,
I still want everyone to enjoy it...

Hmm, then, Luca-chan can choose...?
Or maybe the Princess...?

Alright...!
Let's let Luca-chan decide when she arrives...!

Haha
Looks like the cake will be on hold for a while?
